  creatureName: Vaettir
  image: {fileID: -4762642440264783336, guid: 59b2e3cf4b5a1b94e97a69bab59b2772, type: 3}
  description: "The Vaettir is a creature that lives closer to humans than any other
    creature. \nIt is fairly small, and they live underneath stables, fireplaces
    or even underground passages. Humans that are kind enough to help the Vaettir,
    can be rewarded. \r\n\nBut be wary, the Vaettir can also be vengeful, spreading
    diseases or burning down the farm."
